OL,3,CJLR pauses production on some lines at
OL,4,CSolihull factory
OL,6,FCar manufacturer Jaguar Land Rover has
OL,7,Fconfirmed it is pausing production on
OL,8,Fsome lines at its Solihull factory due
OL,9,Fto challenges with a parts supplier.
OL,11,FIt's understood the pause will cover
OL,12,Fthe annual shutdown for Easter, with
OL,13,Fthe number of days affected totalling
OL,14,Fless than two weeks - and workers will
OL,15,Fstill be going in.
