OL,3,CJLR pauses production on some lines at
OL,4,CSolihull factory
OL,6,FA spokesperson told ITV News Central
OL,7,Fthis evening that JLR was "working
OL,8,Fclosely with that supplier to resolve
OL,9,Fthe issue as quickly as possible and
OL,10,Fminimise any impact on our clients or
OL,11,Four operations."
OL,13,FA JLR spokesperson said: "Due to a
OL,14,Fpart supply challenge with a supplier,
OL,15,Fwe are temporarily pausing production
OL,16,Fon certain vehicle lines at our
OL,17,FSolihull manufacturing facility.
